channel.title: Experimental Turbo FM weekend | Current Game: Colourblind Cop (Canned for the weekend)
channel.description:
i## Welcome this’ll be a little hub page for my experimental shit i do cause i don’t want to spam marl is already mad at me so ok thanks bye Starting at [date=2018-11-24 time=12:00:00 timezone="America/Denver" format="LLL" timezones="Europe/Paris|America/Los_Angeles"]
### Rules
https://forum.imperium42.com/t/forum-of-lies-official-hub/1515
### Gameplay Days 15 minutes long, nights 5 minutes long or unless I get all the actions. 5 civilians 2 Mafia 3 cops (2 colourblind)
You are a Mafia Goon. (Night ability) Kill a player.
You are a Town Civilian. (Passive) You’re useless. just vote people and see what happens.
You are a Town Cop. (Night ability) Check a player to see their alignment.
You are a Town Colourblind Cop. (Passive) you aren’t told you’re color blind. when you flip you’ll be a cop. (Night ability) Check a player for the opposite faction. Town is now scum and scum is now town. muhahahaha.
### Executions To accuse someone say "**/accuse [player]**" or "**/vote [player]**" No trials. Voted up means he’s outta there. Executions end the current day.
### Journals No journals. quit spamming me with journals we're not doing em
### To Join To join, simply express interest in joining by saying something like "I want to join" or "/join" or "/in" or "sign me up, coach" or whatever you want
### Players: 1. @Meteoro 2. 3. @NAOtheRitualist 4. @Frostwolf103 5. @MaximusPrime 6. 7. 8. 9. @GamerPoke
### possibly useful timestamps [game 2 signups ](https://forum.imperium42.com/t/experimental-turbo-fm-weekend-current-game-colourblind-cop-signups-open/73835/566)
